	Manish Narwaria and Weisi Lin.
	
Python Implementation Authors:
	Victor Gonzalez, Priscila Cruz, Andrea Ortega and Susana Dominguez.
	
Context:
	Implementation made for a investigation research for the "Scientific
	Computation 1" class.
	
University:
	Universidad Tecnica Federico Santa Maria, Valparaiso, Chile.
	
Date: June 2012

